These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-4-1::.
3 different games are played: canasta, bridge, whist
There 3 different types of food: eggplant, nectarine, plum
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, fonseca, dunhill
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: romance, superhero, thriller
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, country, funk
House: wooden, modern, victorian
City: hamburg, miami, marseilles
 1. the fan of ambient is the person eating nectarine##1
 2. the fonseca-smoker is on the left or right of the victorian house##3
 3. the person watching superhero movies is on the left or right of the person traveling to marseilles##3
 4. the siglo-smoker is the victorian house##1
 5. the person traveling to hamburg is between the person eating plum and the person playing whist##2
 6. the person playing bridge is in an odd position##4
 7. the person eating plum is on the left or right of the modern house##3
 8. the person watching thriller movies is on the far right##1
 9. the person eating nectarine is between the wooden house and the fan of country##2
10. the person watching superhero movies is the fonseca-smoker##1
11. the person traveling to hamburg is between the person watching thriller movies and the victorian house##2
12. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
13. the person traveling to marseilles is the person playing bridge##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |         3          |
| Game      | whist | canasta     | bridge      |
| Food          | eggplant | nectarine | plum               |
| Cigar           | siglo   | fonseca   | dunhill |
| Movie-Genre   | romance  | superhero | thriller           |
| Music-Genre   | country  | ambient   | funk               |
| House   | victorian  | modern   | wooden           |
| City           | miami   | hamburg      | marseilles              |

