.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-4-2::.
There 3 different types of food: apple, lime, onion
The people have 3 different hobbies: card-games, chess, traveling
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, designer, musician
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, soy-milk, almond-milk
There are 3 different favourite colors: mauve, turquise, amber
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, june, july
The people use 3 different means of transport: ship, quad-bike, boat
 1. the designer is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is traveling##3
 2. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3
 3. the person who's birthday is in july is in an odd position##4
 4. the accountant is the person who's birthday is in july##1
 5. the person driving the boat is the person who likes turquise##1
 6. the person who likes mauve is on the left of the person eating onion##1
 7. the person driving the ship is the person eating apple##1
 8. the person drinking almond-milk is in the middle##1
 9. the person eating apple is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
10. the person who likes turquise is the accountant##1
11. the person who's hobby is chess is the person who likes amber##1
12. the accountant is on the left or right of the musician##3
13. the person driving the boat is on the far right##1
14. the person who likes turquise is in an odd position##4
15. the person who's birthday is in february is the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |
| Food          | lime     | apple      | onion      |
| Hobby         | chess    | traveling  | card-games |
| Job           | designer | musician   | accountant |
| Beverage   | soy-milk     | almond-milk    | iced-tea      |
| Color   | amber  | mauve | turquise    |
| Birthday           | june    | february       | july     |
| Transport         | quad-bike  | ship   | boat   |

