.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-4-4::.
House: farmhouse, modern, art-deco
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, february, october
The people have 3 different jobs:  mechanic, paramedic, scientist
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, documentary, musical
3 different pets are kept: snake, dog, hedgehog
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: basketball, rugby, sailing
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, pall-mall, old-henry
 1. the scientist is the person who's birthday is in june##1
 2. the aristoff-smoker is on the far right##1
 3. the person who's sport is sailing is the person who's birthday is in june##1
 4. the mechanic is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
 5. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the art-deco house##1
 6. the mechanic is the person who's sport is rugby##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in june is the pall-mall-smoker##1
 8. the owner of the hedgehog is the person watching comedy movies##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in february is in an even position##4
10. the person who's birthday is in june is the modern house##1
11. the pall-mall-smoker is the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |      3      |
| House      | modern   | art-deco      | farmhouse      |
| Birthday          | june | february      | october      |
| Job           | scientist  | paramedic  | mechanic    |
| Movie-Genre   | musical    | comedy     | documentary |
| Pet   | dog  | hedgehog      | snake     |
| Sport         | sailing    | basketball | rugby       |
| Cigar     | pall-mall    | old-henry      | aristoff    |

