3 different games are played: mah-jongg, billiard, domino
House: art-deco, wooden, farmhouse
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: basketball, soccer, water-polo
There are 3 different favourite colors: yellow, coral, fuchsia
 1. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far right##1
 2. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
 3. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
 4. the person playing domino is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is gardening##3
 5. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is soccer##3
 6. the person playing billiard is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person who growstulip is the person watching spy movies##1
 8. the person watching animation movies is the person who likes yellow##1
 9. the person who likes fuchsia is in an even position##4
10. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left or right of the person playing domino##3
11. the farmhouse house is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
12. the person who's sport is soccer is the person who growsazalea##1
13. the wooden house is the person playing mah-jongg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |        2        |     3      |
| Hobby         | gardening | chess           | singing    |
| Flower           | azalea     | tulip | lily |
