 4. the person playing monopoly is the person who's birthday is in february##1
 5. the person drinking coffee is the person playing scrabble##1
 6. the person drinking 7up is between the person playing snooker and the person playing scrabble##2
 7. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
 9. the fan of salsa is the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
10. the person eating spinach is between the person eating banana and the person eating cabbage##2
11. the person eating cabbage is on the left of the person eating spinach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2        |       3       |
| Food          | cabbage      | spinach        | banana        |
| Beverage           | coffee | 7up | mirinda    |
| Birthday   | september       | february        | july       |
| Music-Genre   | disco        | rock           | salsa         |
| Game   | scrabble    | monopoly         | snooker          |
| Transport           | trike         | roller           | airplane    |
| Sport         | volleyball   | basketball     | skateboarding |

